{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"handleOpenURL:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","text":"NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL to process."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Test device registration","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Deep link tracking","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"role":"symbol","title":"handleOpenURL:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}